short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Advent of Code Private Leaderboard Daily provides submission times for each participant for each problem.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension enhances the private leaderboard experience on Advent of Code (https://adventofcode.com.) Users with the extension will be able to view submission times for each problem by each member of their leaderboard.
